reviewText: Very good. Touching interviews and review of his work. SRK is a good actor, India icon and worthy of this tribute.

This collection has musical clips from several of Shah Rukh Khan's films...from Darr (1993) up to Kabhi Alvida Naa Kehna (2006). It's wonderful to be able to sit down and enjoy some of the most memorable moments of Shah Rukh Khan's films.
